{"tid":113171,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得自己中左劣質基因 入來討論下","createTime":"2017-02-08T17:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T12:37:23.000Z","uid":54581,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2433f7951176e05c2684277a22c3183d02a1924","tid":113171,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"綜合下樓主自己既劣質基因先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n腸胃差，吸收唔好； 肺功能，血氣差，易氣虛 體力差 ； 腎虧，精神不振<br />\n<br />\n一出世就有白頭髮，先天不足到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樣就似足濕鳩呀嫲，遺傳晒佢近親既 撚屌劣質基因，好後生就有腸胃病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所謂劣幣驅逐良幣，邊個唔明既就叫佢望下我同我呀哥細佬個樣既分別<br />\n<br />\n佢地遺傳綜合晒呀爸呀媽，同母親個邊既優質基因，精力充沛，高大，眉長眼有神鼻樑勁挺.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就隔代遺傳晒呀嫲，同老豆長輩既劣質廢體基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8079f37d9f4f76ef25307c9d936eee7d974fdec9","tid":113171,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d43aed669df5b531afce92c34c5033b25ad2a8","tid":113171,"uid":14036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"中咗大部分阿爸嗰邊嘅劣質基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由細到大都好在意，例如阿媽對眼靚遺傳唔到，但係女真係多數似老豆無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好在愈大愈多人話我同阿媽似樣先開心啲"},{"pid":"e39b8317b2a09f6e392186c6d00f7468b1ca600a","tid":113171,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35737c87e741cddd6240a8447d2ffe4154a9f7a4","tid":113171,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"個樣似老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ba0a51289c0146be1c8170fb4e2730de4bd929","tid":113171,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T22:23:17.000Z","msg":"不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e4815f04755c458cdedf671a6b2495a1e708f4","tid":113171,"uid":5767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T22:36:03.000Z","msg":"老豆：臉上兩粒墨一模一樣仲要幾大粒下<br />\n           濕疹<br />\n老母：鼻敏感<br />\n            哨牙，好彩有樣野叫cool左牙<br />\n爺：極度瘦底成條藤條咁，食極唔肥"},{"pid":"dc36ecd297994fe712006a1071de7243fe93c3c1","tid":113171,"uid":5767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T22:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆：臉上兩粒墨一模一樣仲要幾大粒下<br />\n           濕疹<br />\n老母：鼻敏感<br />\n            哨牙，好彩有樣野叫cool牙<br />\n爺：極度瘦底成條藤條咁，食極唔肥</blockquote>"},{"pid":"59f75625528c2e50b235366e33018ed51d0dd98b","tid":113171,"uid":72091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"遺傳左了老豆既臭狐 老母既扁平足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42abf1122a68c5ba54929c67d852e42fb67bc94c","tid":113171,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遺傳左了老豆既<span style=\"color: red;\">臭狐</span> 老母既扁平足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6447d4a620a88685cbbc44a1686fd1439d28fa2a","tid":113171,"uid":80148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:53:44.000Z","msg":"天生散光 比老母遺傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b842dc2d1246155f0f9c4f1cc211d70e44326d16","tid":113171,"uid":18607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:55:06.000Z","msg":"遺傳老母的矮！"},{"pid":"3ce2f81ef1bbce3519a552295f70de0797b2e235","tid":113171,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:57:23.000Z","msg":"遺傳咗啊爸嘅宅男性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca37edf2d77ae8e3199cf7bdfabde468da5f719","tid":113171,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:06:47.000Z","msg":"樓主d中國人蝗性呢？"},{"pid":"61cd77a3d2536ab2e9215e7993e12b4e5a099b69","tid":113171,"uid":11089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:09:32.000Z","msg":"平胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504a10cf90244a245bca54b3c91d5b95fe2cf31e","tid":113171,"uid":83303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遺傳咗啊爸嘅宅男性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遺傳老母個邊嘅下半身易有脂肪同單眼皮劣質基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩中學用開始用雙眼皮膠水 依家用都有雙眼皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同時遺傳左啊爸個邊食極唔肥的優良基因 所以睇落都算 係下半身同上半身比例差少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0df8ae0a321709194f9108b5ba755b10d645b59","tid":113171,"uid":23238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"遺傳咗阿媽既貧血<br />\n老豆既易肥體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f492d5f26221dba93c072662f5a98cdd2ee8187","tid":113171,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:16:10.000Z","msg":"咁我應該係突變基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaeaf03a3a69cbb368fc1eefdfdfdb33738f5a1f","tid":113171,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:34:14.000Z","msg":"丁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid